        <h2>The World</h2>
        <section>
            <h3>Origins of Chiikawa</h3>
            <figure>
                <img src="../../images/story/ChiikawaWorldMap.png" alt="The World Map of Chiikawa" class="image"/>
                <figcaption>The World Map of Chiikawa</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <p>Long ago, the world of Chiikawa was a land of mystery and wonder. Rolling meadows, snowy mountains, and sparkling seas formed a tapestry of diverse landscapes. Legends say the world was shaped by the dreams of its first inhabitants, who wished for a place where every creature could thrive.</p>
            <h3>Geography and Wonders</h3>
            <p>The Chiikawa world is divided into regions, each with its own climate and character. The central plains are home to the Chiikawa people, while the Hachiware Republic flourishes in the west. The Usagi Union stretches across the northern tundra, and the Kurimanju Kingdom nestles in fertile valleys. The Momonga Empire soars above the clouds, and Rakko lines the southern coasts. Natural wonders abound: the Crystal Lake, the Whispering Woods, and the Skyward Peaks are just a few of the marvels that inspire awe and adventure.</p>
            <h3>Creatures Great and Small</h3>
            <p>From the playful Chiikawa to the wise Hachiware, the world is filled with unique beings. Usagi are known for their speed and cleverness, Kurimanju for their strength and wisdom, Momonga for their curiosity, and Rakko for their adventurous spirit. Each species brings its own traditions, stories, and talents, enriching the world’s culture.</p>
            <h3>Harmony and Conflict</h3>
            <p>Though the world is often peaceful, history is marked by moments of conflict and reconciliation. Wars and civil strife have shaped the nations, but the enduring spirit of friendship and unity prevails. Festivals, councils, and alliances help maintain harmony, and the lessons of the past guide the future.</p>
            <h3>Exploration and Discovery</h3>
            <p>Adventurers roam the land, seeking new horizons and ancient secrets. Explorers map the unknown, scholars study the stars, and inventors create wonders that change daily life. The world of Chiikawa is ever-evolving, with new stories unfolding in every corner.</p>
            <h3>The Future Awaits</h3>
            <p>As the world grows, so do its dreams. The Chiikawa world stands as a testament to the power of hope, creativity, and friendship. Its story is far from over, and every creature—great and small—has a part to play in shaping the chapters yet to come.</p>
        </section>
